=Richard M. Barnhart (1934-)=
==Publications==
===Monographs===
* Marriage of the Lord of the river: A lost landscape by Tung Yüan. Ascona: Artibus Asiae, 1970
* Peach blossom spring : gardens and flowers in Chinese paintings. New York: Metropolitan Museum of Art, 1983
* Along the border of heaven : Sung and Yüan paintings from the C. C. Wang Family Collection. New York: Metropolitan Museum of Art, 1983
* Master of the lotus garden : the life and art of Bada Shanren (1626 - 1705). New Haven: Yale University Press, 1990
* Painters of the Great Ming : the Imperial Court and the Zhe School. Dallas: Dallas Museum of Art, 1993
*  ¬Li¬ Kung-lin's classic of filial piety. New York: Metropolitan Museum of Art, 1993
* The Jade Studio: masterpieces of Ming and Qing painting and calligraphy from the Wong Nan-p'ing Collection. New Haven, Conn.: Yale University Art Gallery, 1994